{"tid":1400444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各區注意，九半之後可以既話去各區鐵路站護送英雄回歸。","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:48:02.000Z","uid":62011,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d512da1ecea8fb81ac7b833101acc46816055f1","tid":1400444,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"根據經驗，死黑警好中意係唔同區等待遊行人士，想睇下係咪捉到人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇出去既人可以去返自己區鐵路站，只要人多就有機會畀遊行人士混入人群去，方便佢哋返屋企。"},{"pid":"a1e1c68263a2d88ae1421cfa2f7aa1392ef96214","tid":1400444,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"帶埋衫畀佢哋方便更換。<br />\n食物，水，錢都唔少得。"},{"pid":"8690645552308bb0dba7d67892b35e8509a7bbcf","tid":1400444,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"大西北，主流轉車站最重要。"},{"pid":"4e9f7caa9e106d7a609483d39b1d128dbbf2300c","tid":1400444,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc67ce6233561b27e4be1fb5fa6f0e458ca52e10","tid":1400444,"uid":266231,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"082eecaf9c0e3f762cc4e42127f1910bcc116459","tid":1400444,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"推到各區睇到。"},{"pid":"18aa351b3da176ee3aae279c62ad2e53c9939e84","tid":1400444,"uid":178368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:15:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e1fc3dc0b1e74299b25839b0fa597767bcc8778a","tid":1400444,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf4c461c55524c2cc3c37a1dd1f346fd661b8ad","tid":1400444,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62065089e56a945d93b64990